INSERT INTO `cmf_plugin_article_item` VALUES ('238', '5', null, '半江春水 柔化夷陵—盛帆2015春游之西陵峡', '0', '', '<p></p>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4月25号，盛帆组织员工前往西陵峡春游赏美景，两天的旅行累并快乐着，游览之后，相信每个人心中都有一个不一样的西陵峡，但毋庸置疑，它是美的。</span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">由财务部罗秀芳所写的游记《半江春水 柔化夷陵》，把已游者再次带回美妙的旅行回忆中，让未游者陶醉其中无限向往....</span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;《半江春水 &nbsp;柔化夷陵》</strong></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ----盛帆财务部罗秀芳</strong></span></section>\r\n</span></span></section>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span>若问闲情都几许？烟波浩渺，满江春意，正值人间四月时！</section>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 想用溪水来形容这水的清透碧绿，可惜溪水没有这样的磅礴气势；想用江水来形容她的迷人气质，又觉得过于妩媚和妖娆，盖过了她的清新与纯洁。半江春水，清纯犹在，胭脂未满。亦如半妆美人，略施粉黛，却不失颜色，一颦一笑，柔化人心。这，就是西陵峡口的水，美得让人心醉。</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/UploadFiles/Images//admin/201504/QQ图片20150429103007.jpg.axd\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;金黄色的大游船，跟两岸碧绿的山峰交相辉映，游船划过的波痕，正躺在中间窃窃密语。山不高，天也不高。山上露出几块岩石，银光闪闪，层层叠叠，错落有致。此时，阳光明媚，看石头也觉得是一种柔情。船上的游人，大多是同事，目不转睛的看着周围的景色，贪婪的呼吸着清透滋润的空气。远离了城市的喧嚣，远离了世俗的纷扰，回归自然，解放身心，重拾自我。此时的西陵峡，有着一双灵气的大眼睛，顾盼生辉，秋波频频，情意绵绵。</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/UploadFiles/Images//admin/201504/4brmjqrz.y4t.jpg.axd\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: small; line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 快艇一路乘风破浪，溅起的雪白水花肆无忌惮的拍打着船体，时不时落在脸上，仿佛是在给人一个个甜蜜的吻。惊叫声，欢呼声，汽艇声，混成一片。千里江陵一日还，恐怕没这个激情吧。疯狂起来的西陵峡，处处洋溢的都是欢声笑语。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;河山大好，景美如画，心情明朗，连胆量也大了很多。小时候最怕的索桥，突然之间也敢在上面毫无顾忌的来回奔跑了。<span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">恐惧在某些情况下不自觉地转化为沉醉与喜爱了。</span><span style=\"font-size: small; line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/UploadFiles/Images//admin/201504/QQ图片20150429103031.jpg.axd\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 走到巴蜀部落，才知道阳春白雪，下里巴人的来源，平时当真也罢，调侃也罢，从来没有去深究过，巴人的部落。常说自己生长在秦巴山下，却没有仔细探索巴山之下的人民与文化。旅游达人常说，去一个城市，首先要去博物馆，了解她的历史与文化。事实证明如此，美景自有人文相配，才不会觉得肤浅。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 白马洞中，很是凉爽，也很潮湿。洞名来源于唐僧西天取经，白龙马寓居于此的传说。传说真也好，假也罢，代表的是当时人们的一种情感与寄托，某些时候算得上是一种信仰。洞中钟乳石些许，涓涓细流从洞顶流淌而下，汇流成地下暗河，乘一叶小舟，便可进出。跟不上队伍的节奏，除了有点阴森害怕外，最大的好处就是可以安静地听到水滴落下时清脆的滴答声，还有自己的脚步回声。</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/UploadFiles/Images//admin/201504/QQ图片20150429103018.jpg.axd\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;山是水的根，水是山的魂。醉翁都可以意不在酒，而我们又怎能忽略这山水的灵气呢？三游洞之后，便要打道回府。良辰美景，又有友人相伴，难怪白居易、元稹他们能写出那么美丽的诗赋。舍与不舍，都要踏上归程。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &ldquo;生活里不能没有笑声，没有笑声的世界该是多么寂寞。什么也改变不了我对生活的热爱，我微笑着走向火热的生活。&rdquo;临行路上，仿佛还听到汪国真先生远在天国的吟诵。宁愿马不停蹄、精疲力竭的在路上，也不愿意无所事事、惶惶度日的无聊中。春意不常在，闲情不常有，恰风华年少，韶光亦不可负。</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>此次春游活动，相信公司员工不仅欣赏了美丽的风景，放松了身心，缓解了工作生活带来的压力，同时还为大家提供了沟通交流的平台，相信在以后的工作中大家会以更加饱满</span><span style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: 1.5em;\">的工作热情</span><span style=\"font-size: medium; line-height: 1.5em;\">投入到自己的工作岗位中，为公司的蓬勃发展贡献自己的力量。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<section class=\"tn-Powered-by-XIUMI\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></section>\r\n<p></p>', '0', '', '', '', 'admin', '', '', '', '', '/UploadFiles/Images//admin/201504/4brmjqrz.y4t.jpg.axd', '', '259', '0', '', '1', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '2015-04-29 00:00:00', '2016-07-15 11:15:34', '2016-07-15 11:15:34', '2015-04-29 16:27:35', '0', '1', '0', '0');
